comments: Podziemski (GSW) places an arm against Booker (PHX) as he goes for the rebound but the contact is marginal.
Goodwin (GSW) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds and GSW retains possession.
Nurkic (PHX) avoids initiating any illegal contact when he contests Podziemski's (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Paul (GSW) commits a take foul on Goodwin (PHX).
Nurkic (PHX) briefly places an arm at Paul's (GSW) side during his drive to the basket and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Goodwin (PHX) places a hand to Curry's (GSW) front as they move over the pick and the contact is marginal.
Saric (GSW) establishes himself in Goodwin's (PHX) path and does not deliver contact.
Nurkic (PHX) trails Podziemski (GSW) defending his driving shot attempt and avoids initiating any illegal contact.
Kuminga (GSW) engages and disengages with Booker (PHX) and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
Saric (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position defending Nurkic (PHX) in the post.
Paul (GSW) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Booker (PHX) immediately slides his hand off of Saric's (GSW) side and marginal contact occurs during the screen.
Saric (GSW) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Curry (GSW) establishes himself in Gordon's (PHX) path and the two players briefly engage and disengage.
Gordon (PHX) briefly rests his hand on Curry's (GSW) body when he receives the pass and as Curry enters his shooting motion, Gordon immediately removes his hand.
Paul (GSW) commits a take foul on Beal (PHX).
Gordon (PHX) brings his arm toward Podziemski's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs during Podziemski's front during his drive in transition.
